1
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:53,320
Come, Yongzi.

2
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,600
Brother Gang.

3
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,360
Yongzi.

4
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,220
Don't blame me.

5
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,480
I caused all of this.

6
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,280
I want

7
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:43,120
to end this in my own way.

8
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,960
Brother.

9
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,220
I grew up without parents.

10
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:52,480
You and Godmother raised me.

11
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,740
I've always been a troublemaker.

12
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,360
I caused you so much trouble.

13
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,210
Every time, you and Godmother went

14
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,280
to fix it.

15
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,000
Later,

16
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,480
I was a scumbag

17
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,960
and got addicted to gambling.

18
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,290
Every time I owed money,

19
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:13,140
you and Godmother cleaned up my mess.

20
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,140
For raising me as your own,

21
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,440
I can never repay you.

22
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,840
For your and Godmother's kindness,

23
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,090
I'll repay you in the next life.

24
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,600
And Yongzi.

25
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,820
Even though I'm older,

26
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,770
you call me Brother.

27
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,880
But as a brother,

28
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,570
I'm a total failure.

29
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,079
You and Xiaofang must live a good life.

30
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,740
You two will definitely be happy.

31
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:57,040
Remember, when you have a baby,

32
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,000
tell the child they have a

33
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,760
Second Uncle.

34
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,160
Do you two remember

35
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,120
when we were in the mine,

36
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,320
what I said?

37
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:16,560
I said I felt really at peace.

38
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,839
I really felt at peace.

39
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,680
Because I saw hope.

40
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,850
I had something to look forward to.

41
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,040
But that hope and future

42
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,400
were shattered by Xiao Tianman.

43
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,000
So,

44
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,650
I'm going to find Xiao Tianman.

45
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:42,480
I'll solve this my own way

46
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,040
and end it all.

47
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,680
Gang, Yong.

48
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:54,760
Here's to you.

49
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,120
To Godmother.

50
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,560
From now on,

51
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,000
live a good life for me.

52
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,760
Xiao Tianman!

53
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,240
Xiao Tianman!

54
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:18,540
I brought the voice recorder you wanted.

55
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:20,720
Get the hell out here.

56
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,480
I was just looking for the three of you.

57
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,240
You came alone, didn't you, Luo Zhengqiang?

58
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,520
You've got guts.

59
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,600
Where are your two brothers?

60
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,370
Where is my voice recorder?

61
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,240
You want the voice recorder?

62
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,120
If you want it, come at us.

63
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,880
Come at the three of us.

64
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,480
The old lady was getting on in years.

65
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,500
She had terminal lung cancer and didn't have long left.

66
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,760
Do you have any humanity?

67
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,450
Don't you have parents?

68
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,280
Shut your mouth.

69
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,170
What are you talking about?

70
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,700
What's this nonsense about mothers?

71
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:23,160
My godmother is gone. She's dead.

72
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,920
What does your godmother's death have to do with me?

73
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,380
I want the voice recorder.

74
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:30,280
Stop pretending.

75
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:34,180
Didn't you tell Liao Fei to kidnap my godmother?

76
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,440
Didn't she die because of that?

77
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:37,880
So,

78
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,960
it all comes down to you.

79
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,610
Luo Zhengqiang.

80
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,240
What do you want to do?

81
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,360
What do I want?

82
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,600
I want to kill you.

83
00:07:58,640 --> 00:07:59,760
On my turf.

84
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:02,040
You want to kill me, Xiao Tianman?

85
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,120
You've got guts.

86
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,360
Try it.

87
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,320
Try it.

88
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,920
Xiao Er. Yes, Mr. Xiao.

89
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,480
Nobody leaves.

90
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,160
Don't be rash. Don't be rash.

91
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,200
Don't move. Don't move.

92
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,000
Xiao Tianman.

93
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,160
This is the last of the explosives I stole.

94
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:23,290
You must give me an explanation today.

95
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,480
Put this down first.

96
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,240
Put it down.

97
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,680
Qiangzi, I really didn't kill Yang Gang's mother.

98
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,080
I really didn't kill her.

99
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,000
Don't talk nonsense.

100
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,330
Don't. Qiangzi, don't.

101
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,340
How about this.

102
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,919
I'll give you a sum of money.

103
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,159
I'll give you a huge sum.

104
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,120
You three brothers can take this money.

105
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,320
Go wherever you want.

106
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,000
Run far away. Okay?

107
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,600
Okay?

108
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,720
Let's make a deal.

109
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,760
Just give that recording pen back to me,

110
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,840
and I'll agree to anything.

111
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,040
What can money buy?

112
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,440
Can money buy my mom back?

113
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,120
Qiangzi.

114
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,560
I'm taking you down with me.

115
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:50,760
Mr. Xiao, let me go.

116
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,530
I killed someone again.

117
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,280
Lao Er.

118
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,040
I promise you.

119
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:10,040
Do one last thing for me.

120
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,720
I'll give you a lot of money

121
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,800
so you can run away.

122
00:10:17,760 --> 00:10:18,560
Alright.

123
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,560
Hurry up. Carry him out. Go.

124
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,560
Zhang, get the recording ready.

125
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,800
I'll take notes.

126
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:48,840
So you released the party involved.

127
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:51,040
Please cooperate.

128
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,720
Zhang, take them to give a statement later.

129
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,660
He killed someone!

130
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,560
Why did you let him go?

131
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,760
How he gets sentenced

132
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,960
depends on the court.

133
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,760
Just wait for the trial.
